<p><img alt="Dress Standards example" height="300" src="Images/Admin_Offices/Student Record and Registration/GradPhoto/DressPic2.png" style="float: right;" width="300" /></p>
<p>BYU-Idaho dress standards apply to all visitors on campus. To invite the Spirit, guests are encouraged to wear Sunday dress to all graduation events. Additionally, while on campus please refrain from wearing the following attire:</p>
<ul>
<li>Shorts</li>
<li>Capris/Gauchos</li>
<li>Flip-Flops</li>
<li>Worn or ragged jeans</li>
</ul>
<p>Please visit the <a href="http://www.byui.edu/studenthonor/" style="color: #38acec;">Student Honor Office</a> for additional information.</p>
